---

Educational content in this app is sourced from publicly available Samoan
language resources including gagana-samoa.com, samoan.ws, the NZ Ministry
for Pacific Peoples, Samoa Tourism Authority, Pacific Learners Education,
The Koko Samoa, and YouTube educators. All video content remains the property
of the original creators and is embedded via YouTube's standard iframe API.

The Samoan language (Gagana Samoa) is a living language and cultural taonga
of the Samoan people. This app is created with deep respect for Samoan
culture, heritage, and the Fa'a Samoa way of life.

Fa'afetai tele lava. 🌺
